{"article_id":"zRKs9gZsg9TlG8Iq","edus":[{"id":0,"text":"On The Record :","depth":2},{"id":1,"text":"President Trump Vs . Private Citizen Trump On Syria","depth":2},{"id":2,"text":"In an official statement , President Trump described the recent chemical attack in Syria as `` reprehensible ''","depth":6},{"id":3,"text":"and went on to argue","depth":7},{"id":4,"text":"the `` heinous actions by the Bashar al-Assad regime are a consequence of the past administration 's weakness and irresolution . ''","depth":7},{"id":5,"text":"In other words , he blamed former President Barack Obama .","depth":5},{"id":6,"text":"Returning to a common theme of his campaign ,","depth":6},{"id":7,"text":"Trump 's statement concluded ,","depth":6},{"id":8,"text":"`` President Obama said in 2012","depth":8},{"id":9,"text":"that he would establish a 'red line ' against the use of chemical weapons","depth":8},{"id":10,"text":"and then did nothing .","depth":7},{"id":11,"text":"The United States stands with our allies across the globe","depth":7},{"id":12,"text":"to condemn this intolerable attack . ''","depth":7},{"id":13,"text":"Trump 's criticism of Obama 's policy on Syria goes back to 2013 .","depth":4},{"id":14,"text":"A private citizen at that time , he argued","depth":5},{"id":15,"text":"that the U.S. should not get involved in the conflict .","depth":5},{"id":16,"text":"On Tuesday , Trump 's statement did not include what - if anything - his administration would do about the recent attack","depth":6},{"id":17,"text":"or what his posture will be toward Assad in light of it .","depth":6},{"id":18,"text":"Press secretary Sean Spicer said","depth":8},{"id":19,"text":"that the president 's statement `` speaks for itself . ''","depth":8},{"id":20,"text":"He said","depth":10},{"id":21,"text":"Trump is meeting with his national security team ,","depth":11},{"id":22,"text":"is `` alarmed '' at what is happening","depth":12},{"id":23,"text":"and that there will be further discussions with allies about the appropriate action .","depth":12},{"id":24,"text":"He added ,","depth":10},{"id":25,"text":"`` I think ,","depth":11},{"id":26,"text":"at this point ,","depth":13},{"id":27,"text":"as things develop ,","depth":13},{"id":28,"text":"I 'm not ready to talk about our next step ,","depth":13},{"id":29,"text":"but we 'll get there soon . ''","depth":13},{"id":30,"text":"Spicer also referenced Obama 's red line comment ,","depth":9},{"id":31,"text":"in which the then-president said ,","depth":10},{"id":32,"text":"`` A red line for us is we start seeing a whole bunch of chemical weapons moving around","depth":12},{"id":33,"text":"or being utilized .","depth":12},{"id":34,"text":"That would change my calculus .","depth":12},{"id":35,"text":"That would change my equation . ''","depth":12},{"id":36,"text":"At the time , Trump did n't say anything about it on Twitter .","depth":6},{"id":37,"text":"It was n't until Syria started dominating the headlines in the summer of 2013","depth":5},{"id":38,"text":"that Trump began weighing in .","depth":5},{"id":39,"text":"Two days after the U.S. concluded","depth":7},{"id":40,"text":"the Assad regime had used chemical weapons ,","depth":7},{"id":41,"text":"Trump tweeted","depth":8},{"id":42,"text":"that the U.S. `` should stay the hell out of Syria . ''","depth":8},{"id":43,"text":"His message :","depth":8},{"id":44,"text":"Stay out ;","depth":9},{"id":45,"text":"Syria is not America 's problem .","depth":9},{"id":46,"text":"And Trump was relatively consistent on that","depth":6},{"id":47,"text":"as the conflict in Syria intensified","depth":7},{"id":48,"text":"and the Obama administration contemplated an expanded U.S. role .","depth":7},{"id":49,"text":"In late August 2013 , the U.S. and international community concluded","depth":8},{"id":50,"text":"that the Syrian government had again used chemical weapons .","depth":8},{"id":51,"text":"The Obama administration was reportedly considering a military strike against Syria","depth":9},{"id":52,"text":"to send a message ,","depth":9},{"id":53,"text":"and private citizen Trump questioned","depth":9},{"id":54,"text":"whether it was worth it .","depth":9},{"id":55,"text":"And","depth":7},{"id":56,"text":"long before he was a candidate ,","depth":8},{"id":57,"text":"Trump was critical of politicians","depth":10},{"id":58,"text":"- including Obama -","depth":10},{"id":59,"text":"for telegraphing their military strategy .","depth":9},{"id":60,"text":"On Aug. 30 , 2013 , a U.S. intelligence assessment found","depth":8},{"id":61,"text":"more than 1,400 Syrians were killed in the chemical weapons attack .","depth":8},{"id":62,"text":"Trump 's tweets focused on how that made the U.S. look .","depth":7},{"id":63,"text":"The next day , Aug. 31 , Obama announced","depth":11},{"id":64,"text":"he would seek congressional approval","depth":12},{"id":65,"text":"to carry out strikes in Syria .","depth":12},{"id":66,"text":"This was widely seen as a way","depth":12},{"id":67,"text":"to back away from the red line","depth":13},{"id":68,"text":"he had drawn ,","depth":13},{"id":69,"text":"putting the responsibility for a decision","depth":13},{"id":70,"text":"to escalate involvement in Syria","depth":13},{"id":71,"text":"on the shoulders of Congress .","depth":12},{"id":72,"text":"It rapidly became clear that Congress was n't going to be able to agree on authorizing force","depth":10},{"id":73,"text":"- and that Congress really did n't want the responsibility .","depth":10},{"id":74,"text":"On Sept. 5 , 2013 , Trump 's concern was that Obama had set the red line in the first place .","depth":8},{"id":75,"text":"A day later ,","depth":11},{"id":76,"text":"seemingly joking ,","depth":12},{"id":77,"text":"Trump offered his own solution :","depth":12},{"id":78,"text":"Use Obamacare in Syria","depth":11},{"id":79,"text":"so `` they would self-destruct . ''","depth":11},{"id":80,"text":"Secretary of State John Kerry ultimately worked out a multinational agreement ,","depth":11},{"id":81,"text":"including Russia ,","depth":11},{"id":82,"text":"in which Assad would agree to give up his chemical weapons .","depth":10},{"id":83,"text":"Trump 's assessment was not positive .","depth":10},{"id":84,"text":"In the end , he concluded","depth":11},{"id":85,"text":"the way","depth":13},{"id":86,"text":"Obama had handled Syria","depth":13},{"id":87,"text":"made America look weak .","depth":12},{"id":88,"text":"That 's a view","depth":11},{"id":89,"text":"President Trump continues to hold ,","depth":11},{"id":90,"text":"as evidenced by the statement","depth":11},{"id":91,"text":"he released on Tuesday .","depth":11}],"relations":[{"parent":183,"left":93,"right":182,"relation":"organization","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":93,"left":0,"right":1,"relation":"organization","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":182,"left":106,"right":181,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":106,"left":103,"right":105,"relation":"context","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":103,"left":96,"right":102,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":96,"left":95,"right":5,"relation":"restatement","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":95,"left":2,"right":94,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":94,"left":3,"right":4,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":102,"left":97,"right":101,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":97,"left":6,"right":7,"relation":"organization","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":101,"left":99,"right":100,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":99,"left":98,"right":10,"relation":"adversative","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":98,"left":8,"right":9,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":100,"left":11,"right":12,"relation":"purpose","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":105,"left":13,"right":104,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":104,"left":14,"right":15,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":181,"left":128,"right":180,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":128,"left":126,"ri